<div class="container">
    <div class="jumbotron"></div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Good News Article Scraper</h1>
    <p>Tired of the same old bad news? We are too. Welcome to the Good News Article Scraper. Click on the button below
        to find articles
        that will keep your mind and soul inspired, make you smile and give you hope in the future of humanity. Sit
        back, take a break, get some
        hot cocoa or coffee and relax with us for 10-30 minutes. Come back whenevery you need another break or
        enlightening story.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <button class="btn-primary" id="scrape" onClick="window.location.reload()">Scrape Articles</button>

        <button class="btn-primary" id="saved">Saved Articles</button>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div id="results">
    {{#each articles}}
    {{#unless saved}}
    <a href="{{link}}" target="_blank">
        <h3>{{title}}</h3>
    </a>
    <button article_id="{{_id}}" title="{{title}}" class="saveArticle btn-success">Save Article</button>
    {{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
    </div>
</div>